###################	demo_ubus_uci_wifi_cfg	###############################
Why:
	Demo how to cfg Wi-Fi params using ubus and uci in OpenWrt platform.

How:
	(a) get using uci directly.
	(b) set using ubus uci, leveraging ucitrack/reload_trigger of procd to
	    apply the changed configuration.

Usage:
	demo_ubus_uci_wifi_cfg <ssid> <get|set> <ifname> [value]

